data.description: Brick greystone 2 flat with finished basement in hot Avondale/Logan Square area! 1st flr features 2br/1ba (GFA/CA) with unheated back porch. The finished basement unit (side and back entrance) 2br/1ba shares GFA/CA with 1st flr. 2nd flr (electric heat) has a 3 br/1ba plus pantry space, also with an additional unheated back porch space. Separate living room and dining room and hardwood flooring are on the 1st and 2nd floor. Close to Logan Square blue line, I-90 expressway, schools, restaurants, gyms, and shopping. Seller is requesting afternoon & evening showings. Selling AS-IS.
